@server_HostAddress = http://localhost:5226

### Public search (before login)
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/public/buses/search?source=Chennai&destination=Bangalore&date=2026-04-23

### Seat availability
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/public/trips/{{tripId}}/seats

### Lock seats for 5 minutes
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/lock-seats
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"tripId": "{{tripId}}",
	"userEmail": "user@example.com",
	"seatNumbers": [1, 2]
}

### Create booking (dummy payment)
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"lockId": "{{lockId}}",
	"userEmail": "user@example.com",
	"paymentMode": "Dummy",
	"passengers": [
		{ "name": "John", "age": 28, "gender": "Male" },
		{ "name": "Jane", "age": 26, "gender": "Female" }
	]
}

### Booking history
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/history/user@example.com

### Cancel booking (12 hours rule, 20% refund)
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/cancel?userEmail=user@example.com

### Upsert profile (SSO field optional)
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"email": "user@example.com",
	"fullName": "John Doe",
	"ssoProvider": "Google"
}

### Register operator
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/operator/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"companyName": "ACME Travels",
	"email": "ops@acme.com",
	"password": "Password@123"
}

### Admin list operators
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/admin/operators

### Admin approve operator
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/admin/operators/{{operatorId}}/approval
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"approve": true,
	"comment": "Approved"
}

### Admin add route
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/admin/routes
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"source": "Chennai",
	"destination": "Coimbatore"
}

### Operator add bus
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/operator/buses
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"operatorId": "{{operatorId}}",
	"busName": "ACME 2+2",
	"capacity": 40,
	"layoutName": "2+2",
	"layoutJson": "{\"rows\":10,\"columns\":4}"
}

### Admin approve bus
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/admin/buses/{{busId}}/approval
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"approve": true,
	"comment": "Bus verified"
}

### Operator add trip
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/operator/trips
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"operatorId": "{{operatorId}}",
	"busId": "{{busId}}",
	"routeId": "{{routeId}}",
	"departureTime": "2026-04-24T21:00:00Z",
	"arrivalTime": "2026-04-25T06:00:00Z",
	"basePrice": 900,
	"platformFee": 35,
	"isVariablePrice": true,
	"pickupPoints": "Koyambedu,Perungalathur",
	"dropPoints": "Madiwala,Majestic"
}

### Operator dashboard
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/operator/{{operatorId}}/dashboard

### Admin disable operator with reason
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/admin/operators/{{operatorId}}/disable
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"reason": "Repeated policy violation"
}

### Notification history for user/operator
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/admin/notifications/user@example.com

GET {{server_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###
